name: HSS website closed
details: HSS website closed until 8 PM (orders after 8 PM can be picked up 6 AM on Sunday)

name: Component Sign-out
details: Larger components must be returned before the end of the event.

name: Pre-Trained Machine Learning Model Declaration
requirements: Make model open source before event
consequences: Disqualification if requirements are not met.

name: Credit Allocation
details: Each team is allocated 300 credits to rent components.

name: Hardware Signout
details: All components must be returned by the end of the event. Sign out components through https://hardware.makeuoft.ca

name: 3D Printing
details: First come, first serve basis. Prints will be done in PLA on the Prusa MINI printers. Prints must be functional.

name: Print Time Limit
details: Prints must be no more than 5 hours in length

name: Print Size Limit
details: Prints must not be larger than 18cm x 18cm x 18cm

name: Print File Types
details: Prints must be submitted as either .3mf or .stl files

name: 3D printing item order
description: Order the corresponding 3D printing item in the Hardware Signout Site for your 3D print to be successfully processed.

name: Fabrication Space Waiver
description: Any hackathon participants wishing to use the Fabrication Space must ﬁll out this waiver form: 2025 MakeUofT Fabrication Space Waiver. Access to the Fabrication Space will be denied without completion of this form.

name: Saturday Lunch
description: Arz Fine Foods Sandwiches (all meats are Halal): Roast Beef Sandwiches, Turkey Sandwiches, Grilled Veg and Halloumi Sandwiches. Gluten-free, Veg, Lactose-free Options Available

name: Saturday Dinner
description: Tasty's Caribbean Cuisine (all meats Halal): Rice and Peas, White Rice, Veggie Chow mein (Sides), Jerk Chicken, BBQ Chicken, Curry Chickpeas (Vegetarian), Curry Potatoes (Vegetarian)

name: Sunday Breakfast
description: Assortment of pastries, cookies and croissants from Metro

name: Sunday Lunch
description: Shawarmas from Tahini’s (all meats are Halal): Chicken Shawarmas, Falafel Shawarmas Available (Vegan and Lactose-free). Gluten-free Sandwiches Available From Subway

name: Wristband
description: Wristband according to your dietary restrictions.

name: Food and Snacks
description: Announcements will be made on Discord once food and snacks are served.

name: Hardware/Mechanical Inventory List
description: Hardware/Mechanical Inventory List (will be updated up to the event)
